messages.messageBody:
Did someone mention they were looking for soy nut butter? I use the I.M.
Healthy brand; I used to mail order it from Whole Foods online, but they
have recently merged with another site and I can't seem to order it. I am
still looking for another place to get it. It does have other ingredients
besides soy nuts (sucanat-cane juice, naturally pressed soybean oil, salt)
that give it a sweeter flavor and better texture. So if you are looking for
just plain soy nut butter, this is not the one. I hope this wasn't the
brand that you tried already but didn't like.

:-)

Olivia
